@startuml activity_tool_invocation_loop

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    BorderColor #6C757D
}

skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
    DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3CD
    DiamondBorderColor #856404
    StartColor #212529
    EndColor #212529
}

skinparam swimlane {
    BorderColor #6C757D
    TitleBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    TitleFontColor #212529
    TitleFontSize 13
}

title Tool Invocation & Tool Call Loop

|Agent / GeneratesText|
start
:Agent.prompt(AgentPrompt);
:Dispatch **PromptingAgent** event;
:Register tool invocation callbacks\n(InvokingTool / ToolInvoked event dispatchers)\nvia gateway.onToolInvocation();
:gateway.generateText(\n  provider, model, instructions,\n  messages, tools, schema,\n  options, timeout\n);

|Gateway / ParsesTextResponses|
:buildTextRequestBody(\n  provider, model, instructions,\n  messages, tools, schema, options\n);

:withErrorHandling → HTTP POST\nto LLM endpoint;

|Error Handling (HandlesFailoverErrors)|
if (HTTP error?) then (yes)
    if (HTTP 429?) then (yes)
        :Throw **RateLimitedException**;
    elseif (HTTP 503?) then (yes)
        :Throw **ProviderOverloadedException**;
    elseif (Insufficient credits?) then (yes)
        :Throw **InsufficientCreditsException**;
    else (other)
        :Throw **AiException**;
    endif
    :Dispatch **ProviderFailedOver** event;
    stop
else (no)
endif

|Gateway / ParsesTextResponses|
:validateTextResponse(data)\n[throws AiException on error/failed status];
:parseTextResponse(data) →\nprocessResponse(data, steps=[], messages=[], depth=0);

note right
  **RECURSIVE LOOP**
  depth increments on each
  tool-call round-trip
end note

repeat
    :Extract from LLM response:\ntext, toolCalls, finishReason,\nusage, citations;
    :Create **Step**(text, toolCalls, [],\n  finishReason, usage, meta);
    :Push Step to steps[];
    :Push **AssistantMessage**(text, toolCalls)\nto messages[];

    if (finishReason == ToolCalls\nAND toolCalls non-empty\nAND depth < maxSteps?) then (yes — continue loop)

        |InvokesTools|
        :executeToolCalls(toolCalls, tools);
        repeat
            :Inspect next **ToolCall**\n(id, name, arguments);
            if (findTool(toolCall.name, tools)\n[match by class_basename]?) then (found)
                :Fire **invokingToolCallback**\n→ Dispatch **InvokingTool** event;
                :tool.handle(new Request(arguments))\n[execute tool logic];
                :Fire **toolInvokedCallback**\n→ Dispatch **ToolInvoked** event;
                :Create **ToolResult**\n(id, name, arguments, result, resultId);
            else (not found)
                :Skip ToolCall\n(no matching tool);
            endif
        repeat while (more ToolCalls?) is (yes)
        ->no;

        |Gateway / ParsesTextResponses|
        :Update current Step:\nreplace with Step(text, toolCalls,\n  **toolResults**, finishReason, ...);
        :Push **ToolResultMessage**(toolResults)\nto messages[];
        :continueWithToolResults(\n  ..., depth + 1\n):\nbuildFollowUpRequestBody();
        :withErrorHandling → HTTP POST\nto LLM endpoint\n[same timeout preserved];
        :validateTextResponse(data);
        note right
          Re-enter loop with
          depth = depth + 1
        end note

    else (no — exit loop)
    endif

repeat while (finishReason == ToolCalls\nAND toolCalls non-empty\nAND depth < maxSteps?) is (yes — loop)
->no — done;

:Build final response:\n**TextResponse** or **StructuredTextResponse**\nwith all steps, toolCalls, toolResults;

|Agent / GeneratesText|
:Wrap TextResponse into\n**AgentResponse**\n(steps, toolCalls, toolResults, messages);
:Dispatch **AgentPrompted** event;
:Return **AgentResponse** to caller;
stop

@enduml
